Package: CompositionalNAimp
Type: Package
Title: Missing Value Imputation with Compositional Data
Version: 1.0
Date: 2026-03-25
Authors@R: person("Michail", "Tsagris", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "mtsagris@uoc.gr")
Author: Michail Tsagris [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Michail Tsagris <mtsagris@uoc.gr>
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports: Compositional, Rfast, Rnanoflann
Suggests: Rfast2
Description: Functions to perform missing value imputation with compositional data using the Jensen-Shannon divergence k--NN algorithm. The functions are based on the following paper: 
             Tsagris M., Alenazi A. and Stewart C. (2026). "A Jensen--Shannon divergence based k--NN algorithm for missing value imputation in compositional data". 
             Journal of Applied Statistics (Accepted for publication).
License: GPL (>= 2)

